bug.short_desc: Beginning of highlighted change in code is not started from absolute zero position in the row

long_desc.thetext:
Steps to reproduce: Hard to say, I've noticed it when displaying a diff.
Actual result: See attached screen shot. The beginning of highlighted change in code is not stared from absolute zero position in the row. It happens as on left as on right side. All the more, it is visible on page with a lot of changes.
OpenGrok 0.10-rc, Apache Tomcat 6.0.29, Sun Java 6 1.6.0_20-b02, Debian GNU/Linux 5.0, Mac OS X 10.6.5, Chrome 8
